{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8f651f52f9","title":"关于向朝鲜赠送冬服的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"91d3276fca","index":0,"year":1952,"month":8,"day":23,"articleId":"8f651f52f9"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"32f3e57bd6","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8f651f52f9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1952年8月，朝鲜民主主义人民共和国政府提出，朝鲜今冬有60万人没有冬衣，希望中国帮助解决，至少帮助解决一半。中国人民志愿军副司令员洪学智于8月18日、22日先后两次将朝方要求电告彭德怀。毛泽东在看了洪学智8月22日的电报后写了这个批语。8月28日，外交部草拟以周恩来名义给中国驻朝临时代办甘野陶的电报，答复朝方提出的要求，毛泽东在审阅这个电报稿时加写了以下文字：“请告朝鲜政府，此三十万套棉衣作为赠送，不要付款，也不要记帐。”"},{"id":"c45949155d","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8f651f52f9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席、中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9394ccaf25","type":"title","text":"关于向朝鲜赠送冬服的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8f651f52f9"},{"id":"32f3e57bd6","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：开方套冬服，可作赠送。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8f651f52f9"},{"id":"c45949155d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8f651f52f9"},{"id":"66652b7f39","type":"paragraph","text":"八月廿三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8f651f52f9"}],"page":{"id":"de642f5fc1","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8f651f52f9","start":207,"end":207}}}},"__N_SSG":true}